name: White Aura Biphamet
description:
1 Tuner Synchro Monster + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
When this card is Synchro Summoned during your turn: You can Special Summon 1 "Divine Dragon Token" (Fish/WATER/Level 10/ATK 3300/DEF 3000) in Defense Position. Once per opponent's turn, if you control no Tokens (Quick Effect): You can Special Summon 1 "Divine Dragon Token". If this card you control is destroyed by an opponent's card effect and sent to your GY, and you control a "Divine Dragon Token": You can Special Summon this card in Defense Position.
